&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err-http2-pseudo-headers/"&gt;ERR_HTTP2_PSEUDO_HEADERS&lt;/a&gt; — invalid pseudo-headers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err-http1-status-code/"&gt;ERR_HTTP1_STATUS_CODE&lt;/a&gt; — invalid HTTP/1.1 status code.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err_http_invalid_status_code/"&gt;ERR_HTTP_INVALID_STATUS_CODE&lt;/a&gt; — invalid status code.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>